                    <div class="columns">
                        <em>Thinking on both sides of the brain.</em>
                        Numbers and colors - logic and beauty - the balance of an equation and the balance of a design. 
                        I offer a rational, problem-solving mathematical background and a lifelong desire to be an artist. 
						<em>Motivated by perfection.</em>
                        Maybe perfection is unattainable, but it can be pursued.  I don't care to assume it can't be found just because I haven't found it yet. <br/>
						<em>Want to know more?</em> <br/>  You can view my <a href="edp-res-geek.pdf">r&eacute;sum&eacute;</a>.
